*snakeoil-0.5 (05 Aug 2012)

  05 Aug 2012; Brian Harring <ferringb@gentoo.org> -snakeoil-0.4.5.ebuild,
  +snakeoil-0.5.ebuild:
  New version including whirlpool/sha512 support, parallelization of
  compression,
  and generally a boatload of functionality that should've been released
  earlier.

